Review Text:
I ordered one full chicken tawa biryani for 2 people. But the quantity I recieved was not even enough for 1 person. There was no raita or curry in the package. Just few onion rings were all I found as add-ons.
There was a small chicken leg which was not at all cooked. Stale taste was coming. When we order a full biryani, we expect 2 chicken pieces. But here the both the quantity and quality of chicken were compromised.
The rice had a different smell, not of biryani.
Very bad experience. Wouldn't order from this place again. It was a waste of money.

Ordered chicken Biryani from Zomato which had almost 50 min to reach to hi-tech city.
Biryani was okayish to order once, its not the Hyderabadi dum biryani what you think which is less spicy and north style.
